val (mouse, fly, worm) = ("Mus musculus","Drosophila melanogaster","Caenorhabditis elegans")
val mouse_genes = models.where($"organism" === mouse)
val fly_genes= models.where($"organism" === fly)
val worm_genes = models.where($"organism" === worm)
val good_models_genes = models.where($"organism".isin(mouse, fly, worm))
